	   <tr><td colspan=2>The information above is far from the truth. To set the record straight, each dragon drops a certain type of armor. For example: Bratavar, Karkona, and Nintal all may drop the mantle. In addition, these three dragons are level 53 (Bratavar) to level 58 (Karkona). The only armor piece they can drop is the mantle. It does not always drop, and when it does, only 1 drops at a time. When a mantle does drop, it could be anything from a Worked Dragonwing Mantle to a Matchless Dragonwing Mantle.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
